<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.229608>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18 – 31. Diestramimini. 18, Diestramima minor, female subgenital plate, ventral view; 19 – 20, Diestramima major: 19, male genitalia, dorsal view; 20, the same, ventral view; 21 – 24, Megadiestramima intermedia: 21, male genitalia, dorsal view; 22, the same, ventral view; 23, apex of male abdomen, dorsal view; 24, the same, lateral view; 25 – 28, Leodiestramima exculta: 25, female subgenital plate, ventral view; 26, male genitalia, dorsal view; 27, the same, ventral view; 28, apex of male abdomen, lateral view; 29 – 31, Mimadiestra biloba sp. nov.: 29, apex of male abdomen, lateral view; 30, the same, dorsal view; 31, male genitalia, ventral view. (Figs 18 – 20, 25 – 28 after Gorochov, 1998; Figs 21 – 24 after Gorochov & Storozhenko, 1992; Figs 29 – 31 original)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/229608/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

